descriptionHtml:
The Pandycat Manor
by [MMF]Pandycat

Located in beneath the Azura\'s shrine.
Containing a Lobby Girl, a humble dog, a seductive shopkeeper, female slaves and a mine to dig more minerals.
Also, The warp doors to the whole of the skyrim are ready to go!!

==== How to get to the Pandycat Manor ====
Open a door at the bottom of the Azura\'s shrine.
or just type
coc PandycatManor
in console.

==== update history ====
1.191
Fixed the transform of the castle Dour in Solitude

1.19
The entrance to the Pandycat Manor, in beneath the Azura\'s shrine, is now rbuilt !!

1.18
A crafting tanning rack is deployed.
In-house shop keeper now deals more foods, various ingredients, daedra hearts, dragon scales & teeth, and more books.

1.15
fixed some minor problem around the navmeshes.
added more ore for the in-house keeper\'s item lists.
change the entrance door to a better looking one.

1.1
added \"The hall of Mannequin\". Lots of Super-Real Mannequin are ready!! Put your stuffs on them!!!

-----

This house contains some stuffs as follows:
-A Lobby Girl
-A humble dog
-A seductive inhouse shop keeper
-The all common stuffs for smithing.
-The Workbench for enchanting
-The Workbench for alchemy
-Player Mannequin
-2 female slaves
-Sword racks, Book shelfs, Dagger cases
-Magical Smithing Workbench for Daedric Stuffs
-Mines to dig more minerals.
-In-door garden to harvest some ingredients
-Some planters of Potatos and Cabbages
-Staff Canteen with cooking devices
-The warp doors to the whole of the Skyrim

==== install ====
The file is just a 1 esp file. Apply esp as usual with your ModManeger.
